Title: Don't Tell Annalise
Writer: Peter Nowalk (created by), Erika Green Swafford, Erika Harrison (executive story editor), Fernanda Coppel (story editor), Morenike Balogun (story editor)
Actors: Viola Davis, Billy Brown, Alfred Enoch, Jack Falahee
Plot: A young client's fate is up in the air after incriminating evidence against Annalise is revealed to the Philadelphia Bar Association's disciplinary board. Meanwhile, Frank's shocking behavior has consequences for someone he knows well.
